### Register a new Student User and Student Record
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register-student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student.john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "studentPassword123!",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "institutionId": 1, // Optional: Replace with a valid institution ID if needed
  "gradeLevel": "10th Grade" // Optional
}

### Register another student (minimal data)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register-student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student.jane.smith@example.com",
  "password": "anotherStudentPass#",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith"
  // institutionId and gradeLevel are optional
}